{"tid":226234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(狗鐵) 荃灣線車廂現\"批鬥座\"貼紙 [369]","createTime":"2017-05-02T11:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T11:21:07.000Z","uid":78900,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80c3cf8c14b7d6353ff4918fc900e3becf6c5f93","tid":226234,"uid":78900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"港鐵自推出「優先座」後，爭議不斷，近年更屢有乘客因坐上而被人拍片招致「網絡批鬥」。《香港01》記者昨晚（30日）在港鐵荃灣線車廂中，發現有人貼上模仿「優先座」貼紙設計的「批鬥座」貼紙。<br />\n港鐵今日回覆指，暫無收到乘客報告有關情況，有關行為違反哪一條港鐵附例，難以一概而論，但《港鐵附例》32條可作參考，該條文寫明違規者最高可被罰款5,000元及監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kb31W5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkb31W5Y.jpg&h=07a0ef60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6K2P4R0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6K2P4R0.jpg&h=6433f8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貼紙顏色圖案與「關愛座」相同<br />\n<br />\n記者昨日晚上7時30分左右，在一列荃灣線往中環方向列車車廂內，發現「批鬥座」貼紙，不論顏色、圖案均和「關愛座」設計幾乎相同，唯一的分別，就是貼紙上的字樣，由「優先座」換成「批鬥座」。剛剛過去的年宵市場，亦曾有人設計過「批鬥座」貼紙攬枕，並在維園攤位出售。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>邊位巴打做架, 好出黎認左去 </strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/87908/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E7%8F%BE-%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5%E5%BA%A7-%E8%B2%BC%E7%B4%99-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E5%80%98%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B%E5%BC%B5%E8%B2%BC%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE5000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F87908%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25B7%259A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5-%25E5%2580%2598%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE5000&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KitibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b9981aad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/87908/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E7%8F%BE-%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5%E5%BA%A7-%E8%B2%BC%E7%B4%99-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E5%80%98%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B%E5%BC%B5%E8%B2%BC%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE5000</a>"},{"pid":"60625459b6b96c199b97e6e98bb71b514e08e2f5","tid":226234,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adac27899f585fd6e34076d7f8cb088c32c13af","tid":226234,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eeb3b40df16f902d4cc6b5a33026769584c692c","tid":226234,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"又咁岩有01記者影到？<br />\n自己痴完自己造新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d5ecfcca2eb51374959e860b4a7c2937b21b7d","tid":226234,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又咁岩有01記者影到？<br />\n自己痴完自己造新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記者在港鐵車廂發現批鬥座貼紙</span>。（梁煥敏攝）  <br />\n好可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}